Name: Cardamom seed, dried, ground
Description: Ground spice commonly used in Indian cooking and drinks, in Middle Eastern cooking and in Scandinavian baking

Name: Chilli (chili), dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground red pepper, characterised by a hot sensation when consumed as a spice.

Name: Cinnamon, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground bark or quills of Cinnamomum verum, C. zeylanicum or C. aromaticum, used as a spice.

Name: Cloves, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground, unopened flower buds of Syzygium aromaticum, used as a spice.

Name: Coriander seed, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground fruit or seed of Coriandrum sativum, used as a spice.

Name: Cumin (cummin) seed, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground fruit or seeds of Cuminum cymimum, used as a spice.

Name: Curry powder
Description: Dried and ground mixture of spices for use in the preparation of Indian-style meals. Typical ingredients include the spices cumin, coriander seed and turmeric.

Name: Fenugreek seed, dried
Description: Dried fenugreek seeds used as a spice.

Name: Ginger, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground rhizome of Zingiber officinale, used as a spice.

Name: Mustard powder
Description: Dry powder composed of ground yellow mustard seeds, for use in preparation of mustard paste or incorporation into other foods.

Name: Nutmeg, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground seed of Myristica fragrans (M. officinalis or M. aromatica), used as a spice.

Name: Oregano, dried
Description: Dried, and sometimes ground, leaves of Oreganum vulgare, used as a culinary herb.

Name: Paprika, dry powder
Description: Dried and ground fruit of red capsicums (sweet red peppers).

Name: Pepper, black, ground
Description: Dried and ground unripe fruit of the pepper tree (Piper nigrum), used as a spice.

Name: Rosemary, dried
Description: Dried woody herb with fragrant needle-like green leaves on small stalks.

Name: Sage, dried
Description: Dry leaves of Salvia officinalis used as a herb.

Name: Thyme, dried, ground
Description: Dried, and sometimes ground, leaves of Thymus vulgaris, used as a culinary herb.

Name: Turmeric, dried, ground
Description: Dried and ground rhizome of Curcuma domestica or C. longa, used as a spice.

Name: Salt substitute, potassium chloride
Description: Product sold as a replacement for regular table salt, containing predominantly potassium chloride.

Name: Salt, table, iodised
Description: Fine granules of sodium chloride sold for direct addition to foods, to which iodine has been added in the form of potassium iodate or iodide. May contain free-flowing agents.

Name: Salt, table, non-iodised
Description: Fine granules of sodium chloride sold for direct addition to foods. May contain free-flowing agents and small amounts of other minerals such as potassium.

Name: Stock, dry powder or cube
Description: Concentrated meat stock that is dried and supplied as a powder or compressed into a cube. Contains ingredients such as salt and flavours.

Name: Taco seasoning mix, chilli-based
Description: Powdered product intended for addition to meat and other ingredients to prepare Mexican-style dishes such as taco filling. Typical ingredients include salt, sugar, maize starch, spices, chilli and citric acid.

Name: Baking powder, dry powder
Description: Fine white powder used to chemically leaven baked goods such as cakes. Composed of 50% cream of tartar, 25% baking soda, and 25% starch.

Name: Baking soda (bicarbonate), dry powder
Description: Fine white powder used to chemically leaven baked goods such as cakes.

Name: Cream of tartar, dry powder
Description: Purified, crystallised potassium bitartrate, used as the acid component of some fast acting baking powder mixtures.

Name: Gelatine, all types
Description: Unflavoured light yellow granular proteinaceous powder. Used to sweeten and thicken soups, sauces and desserts.

Name: Gluten, from wheat (vital wheat gluten)
Description: Protein rich extract of wheat flour.

Name: Starch, potato
Description: Fine powder composed of polysaccharides derived from the potato tuber.

Name: Vanilla, artificial or imitation
Description: Solution containing the substance vanillin, used as a flavouring agent.

Name: Vanilla bean extract
Description: Alcoholic extract of the vanilla bean (Vanilla plantifolia or V. tahitensis), used as a flavouring agent.

Name: Yeast, dry powder
Description: A cream or pale grey powder with a fine, smooth texture. Active raising agent used domestically to leaven a wide range of breads, cakes and pastries.

Name: Beer, high alcohol (5% v/v & above)
Description: Alcoholic beverage characterised by the presence of hops or preparations of hops, prepared by the yeast fermentation of an aqueous extract of malted or unmalted cereals (usually barley), using warm temperature fermentation. Greater than or equal to 5% v/v alcohol.

Name: Beer, full strength (alcohol 4-4.9% v/v)
Description: Alcoholic beverage characterised by the presence of hops or preparations of hops, prepared by the yeast fermentation of an aqueous extract of malted or unmalted cereals (usually barley), using low fermentation temperatures. Alcohol content between 4-4.9% v/v alcohol.

Name: Beer, full strength (alcohol 4-4.9% v/v), carbohydrate modified
Description: Alcoholic beverage characterised by the presence of hops or preparations of hops, prepared by the yeast fermentation of an aqueous extract of malted or unmalted cereals (usually barley), resulting in lower final carbohydrate levels than regular beer.  Alcohol content between 4 - 4.9% v/v alcohol.

Name: Beer, mid-strength (alcohol 3-3.9% v/v)
Description: Alcoholic beverage characterised by the presence of hops or preparations of hops, prepared by the yeast fermentation of an aqueous extract of malted or unmalted cereals (usually barley), so as to restrict alcohol formation or to remove alcohol after fermentation. Products are described on label as mid strength. Alcohol content between 3-3.9% v/v alcohol.

Name: Beer, light (alcohol 1- less than 3% v/v)
Description: Alcoholic beverage characterised by the presence of hops or preparations of hops, prepared by the yeast fermentation of an aqueous extract of malted or unmalted cereals (usually barley), so as to restrict alcohol formation or to remove alcohol after fermentation. Products are described on label as Light or Lite. Alcohol content between 1-<3% v/v alcohol.

Name: Alcoholic beverage, spirit, approximately 40% v/v, all (Brandy, Gin, Rum, Vodka and Whisky)
Description: Includes beverages obtained from the distillation of wine or fermented sugar, cereals or potatoes, or the fermented preparation of grapes or grape products.

Name: Alcoholic beverage, spirit, approximately 30% v/v, all (Brandy, Gin, Rum, Vodka and Whisky), cooked
Description: Includes beverages obtained from the distillation of wine or fermented sugar, cereals or potatoes, or the fermented preparation of grapes or grape products, that has been heated until a large proportion of alcohol has evaporated.

Name: Cider, apple (alcohol approximately 4-5% v/v)
Description: Alcoholic beverage prepared from fermented apples with significant residual sugars. Includes cider produced in Australia, New Zealand and Denmark. Approximately 4% alcohol.

Name: Wine, red, cabernet sauvignon
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the cabernet sauvignon grape, with prolonged grape skin contact to produce wine of a deep red colour. Includes wine produced in Australia. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, red, merlot
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the merlot grape, with prolonged grape skin contact to produce wine of a deep red colour. Includes wine produced in Australia and New Zealand. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, red, pinot noir
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the pinot noir grape, with prolonged grape skin contact to produce wine of a deep red colour. Includes wine produced in Australia and New Zealand. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, red, shiraz
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the shiraz grape, with prolonged grape skin contact to produce wine of a deep red colour. Includes wine produced in Australia only. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, red
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice with prolonged grape skin contact to produce wine of a deep red colour. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, red, cooked
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice with prolonged contact with grape skins, that has been heated until the majority of alcohol has evaporated.

Name: Wine, red, sparkling
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from red wine grapes, retaining significant quantities of dissolved carbon dioxide. Approximately 13% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, rose
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice so that the wine has a pale pink colour. Includes wine produced in Australia and New Zealand. Approximately 13% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, sauvignon blanc
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the sauvignon blanc grape, produced with little contact with grape skins so that the wine is pale yellow in colour with little sugars remaining. Includes wine produced in Australia and New Zealand. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, semillon
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice from the semillon grape, produced with little contact with grape skins so that the wine is pale yellow in colour with little sugars remaining. Includes wine produced in Australia only. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, chardonnay
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice produced from the chardonnay grape, with little contact with grape skins so that the wine is pale yellow in colour with little sugars remaining. Includes wine produced in Australia. Approximately 13% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, riesling
Description: Alcoholic beverage prepared by fermentation of grape juice produced from the riesling grape, with little contact with grape skins so that the wine is pale yellow in colour with some sugars remaining. Includes wine produced in Australia. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice, produced with little contact with grape skins so that the wine is pale yellow in colour. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, cooked
Description: Alcoholic beverage produced by fermentation of grape juice with little contact with grape skins, then heated until the majority of alcohol has evaporated.

Name: Wine, white, sparkling
Description: Alcoholic beverage prepared by fermentation of grape juice produced with little grape skin contact so that the wine is pale yellow in colour and retains significant quantities of dissolved carbon dioxide. Includes wine described as brut or semi-brut in style produced in Australia and France. Approximately 12% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, white, sweet dessert style
Description: Alcoholic beverage prepared by fermentation of grape juice with little grape skin contact, so that the wine is golden in colour and retains a high level of residual sugars (approximately 10% sugars). Includes botrytised wine produced in Australia and New Zealand. Approximately 10% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, fortified, port
Description: Sweet, alcoholic beverage prepared from fermented grape juice to which additional alcohol is added. Approximately 16% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, fortified, sherry, dry style (approximately 1% sugars)
Description: Fermented grape juice to which additional alcohol is added and with a low sugars content (approximately 1%). Approximately 18% v/v alcohol.

Name: Wine, fortified, sherry, sweet style (approximately 11% sugars)
Description: Fermented grape juice to which additional alcohol is added and with a high sugars content (approximately 11%) and a sweet flavour. Approximately 17.0% v/v alcohol.

Name: Cocoa powder
Description: Powder produced from the liquor extracted from cocoa beans. Typically used to flavour beverages and in baking.

Name: Beverage base, chocolate flavour, added vitamins A, B1, B2, C & D, Ca & Fe (Milo)
Description: Dry beverage base used to prepare a chocolate flavoured beverage with the addition of milk. Contains added iron, calcium and vitamins A, B1, B2, C and D. Typical ingredients include malted cereals, milk solids and cocoa. Milo brand is an example of such a product.

Name: Beverage, chocolate flavour, from Milo powder, with regular fat cows milk
Description: Beverage prepared by mixing milo powder with regular fat cows milk.

Name: Beverage base, drinking chocolate, unfortified
Description: Unfortified powdered mixture of sugar and cocoa or chocolate used for mixing with milk or water to produce a beverage. Other ingredients may include maltodextrin, milk solids, soy lecithin, salt, flavour.

Name: Beverage, chocolate flavour, from drinking chocolate, with regular fat cows milk
Description: Beverage prepared by mixing drinking chocolate powder with regular fat cows milk.

Name: Coffee, instant, dry powder or granules
Description: Dried extract of coffee beans, used to produce a beverage by the addition of boiling water.

Name: Coffee, black, from instant coffee powder
Description: Beverage made from instant coffee powder or granules to which boiling water is added. Does not contain added milk, sugar or flavour.

Name: Coffee, instant, dry powder or granules, decaffeinated
Description: Dried extract of decaffeinated coffee beans, used to produce a beverage by the addition of boiling water.

Name: Coffee, black, from instant coffee powder, decaffeinated
Description: Beverage made from instant decaffeinated coffee powder or granules to which boiling water is added. Does not contain added milk, sugar or flavour.

Name: Coffee, espresso, from ground coffee beans
Description: Beverage prepared from ground coffee beans and a small amount of hot water, as purchased in takeaway outlets or restaurants. Does not contain added milk, sugar or flavour.

Name: Coffee, cappuccino, from ground coffee beans, with regular fat cows milk
Description: Beverage prepared from a serve of espresso style coffee to which a large amount of heated and aerated regular fat cows milk is added and sprinkled with chocolate. Does not contain added sugar or flavour.

Name: Coffee, flat white or latte, from ground coffee beans, with regular fat cows milk
Description: Beverage prepared from a serve of espresso style coffee to which a large amount of heated and aerated regular fat cows milk is added. Does not contain added sugar or flavour.

Name: Coffee, long black, from ground coffee beans
Description: Beverage prepared from ground coffee beans to which a large volume of hot water is added. Does not contain added milk, sugar, or flavour.

Name: Cordial base, 25% citrus fruit juice, regular
Description: Concentrated sugar-based syrup containing a minimum of 25% citrus fruit juice (typically orange or lemon juice), used to prepare a beverage by dilution with water.

Name: Cordial, 25% citrus fruit juice, regular, recommended dilution
Description: Non-alcoholic beverage prepared by mixing 1 part of a concentrated sugar syrup containing 25% citrus fruit juice with 4 parts of water.

Name: Cordial base, 40% citrus fruit juice, regular
Description: Concentrated sugar-based syrup containing at least 40% citrus fruit juice (typically orange or lemon juice), used to prepare a beverage by dilution with water.

Name: Cordial, 40% citrus fruit juice, regular, recommended dilution
Description: Non-alcoholic beverage prepared by mixing 1 part of a concentrated sugar syrup containing 40% non-citrus fruit juice with 4 parts of water.

Name: Cordial base, 5% blackcurrant juice, regular
Description: Concentrated sugar-based syrup containing a minimum of 5% blackcurrant juice, used to prepare a beverage by dilution with water.

Name: Cordial, 25% blackcurrant juice, regular, recommended dilution
Description: Non-alcoholic beverage prepared by mixing 1 part of a concentrated sugar syrup containing blackcurrant juice with 5 parts of water.

Name: Fruit drink, apple juice
Description: Commercially prepared product made from 25% apple juice or puree, water, sugars and food acids. Does not contain added vitamin C.

Name: Fruit drink, cranberry
Description: Commercially prepared beverage made from approximately 25% cranberry juice, water and sugar.

Name: Fruit drink, orange juice
Description: Commercially prepared beverage made from 25% orange juice with added water, sugar and food acid. Does not contain added vitamin C.

Name: Juice, apple, commercial, added vitamin C
Description: Commercial beverage prepared by crushing apples and filtering or clarifying the resultant juice. Contains added vitamin C. Does not contain added sugar.

Name: Juice, apple & blackcurrant, commercial
Description: Commercial beverage prepared from crushed apples and blackcurrants. Does not contain added sugar.

Name: Juice, lemon
Description: Commercial or homemade liquid prepared from the endocarp of lemons.

Name: Juice, lime
Description: Commercial or homemade liquid prepared from the endocarp of limes.

Name: Juice, orange, commercial
Description: Commercial beverage sold chilled which is prepared from the endocarp of oranges. Contains added vitamin C, but does not contain added sugar.

Name: Juice, orange & mango, commercial
Description: Commercial beverage prepared from 95% orange juice and 5% mango juice. Contains added vitamin C, but does not contain added sugar.

Name: Mineral water, natural, unflavoured
Description: Carbonated or naturally sparkling ground water obtained from subterranean water-bearing strata that, in its natural state, contains soluble matter. No added sugar or flavours.

Name: Mineral water, citrus flavoured
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage containing 5% citrus juice (orange and lemon), mineral water and sugar.

Name: Soft drink, cola flavour
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage containing water, sugar, cola flavour, caffeine and colours.

Name: Soft drink, cola flavour, decaffeinated
Description: Decaffeinated, carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage containing water, sugar, cola flavour.

Name: Soft drink, cola flavour, intense sweetened or diet
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage containing water, intense sweeteners, cola flavour, caffeine and colours.

Name: Soft drink, cola flavour, intense sweetened or diet, decaffeinated
Description: Decaffeinated, carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage containing water, intense sweeteners, cola flavour and colours.

Name: Soft drink, energy drink, Red Bull
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic water-based flavoured beverage containing added caffeine, taurine, glucuronolactone, inositol, niacinamide, pantothenic acid, vitamins B6 and B12.

Name: Soft drink, energy drink, V
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic water-based flavoured beverage containing added caffeine, taurine, guarana, inositol, glucoronolactone, pantothenic acid, vitamins B2, B3, B6 and B12. May also contain ginkgo bilboa extract.

Name: Soft drink, lemonade and fruit flavours
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage prepared from water, sugar and citric acid.

Name: Soft drink, lemonade and fruit flavours, intense sweetened or diet
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage prepared from water, intense sweetener, fruit flavours and colours.

Name: Soft drink, tonic water
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage prepared from water and sugar with added quinine.

Name: Soft drink, tonic water, intense sweetened or diet
Description: Carbonated, non-alcoholic beverage prepared from water and intense sweetener with added quinine.

Name: Tea, green, plain, without milk
Description: Beverage prepared by brewing green, unfermented tea leaves in hot water, either as loose tea leaves or encased in porous teabags. Tea is not decaffeinated or flavoured. Does not contain added milk or sugar.

Name: Tea, regular, black, brewed from leaf or teabags, without milk
Description: Beverage prepared by brewing black tea leaves (dried, fermented leaves of Camellia sinensis) in hot water, either as loose tea leaves or encased in porous teabags. Tea is not decaffeinated or flavoured. Does not contain added milk or sugar.

Name: Tea, decaffeinated, black, brewed from leaf or teabags, without milk
Description: Beverage prepared by brewing black decaffeinated tea leaves (dried, fermented leaves of Chrysanthemum species) in hot water, either as loose tea leaves or encased in porous teabags. Tea is not flavoured. Does not contain added milk or sugar.

Name: Water, bottled, still
Description: Still, non-carbonated water bottled prior to sale. May include spring water.

Name: Water, tap
Description: Water as supplied through the municipal water system. Values are approximations of those reported across Australia, and may vary according to location or time of year.

Name: Water, soda
Description: Carbonated water.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, rice cracker, plain
Description: Commercially prepared savoury biscuit made predominantly from rice flour, without added flavourings.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, rice cracker, seaweed flavoured
Description: Commercially prepared savoury biscuit made predominantly from rice flour, with added seaweed flavourings.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, rice cracker, flavoured (excluding cheese or seaweed)
Description: Savoury biscuit made predominantly from rice flour, with added flavourings such as BBQ, chicken and salt and vinegar. Does not include seaweed, cheese or sour cream flavoured rice crackers.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from white wheat flour, cheese-flavoured
Description: Commercially prepared savoury small biscuit made from white wheat flour, with added fat and cheese flavourings.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from white wheat flour, flavoured (excluding cheese)
Description: Commercially prepared savoury small biscuit made from white wheat flour, with added fat and flavourings other than cheese.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from white wheat flour, plain snack cracker style
Description: Commercially prepared, small, plain savoury biscuit made from white wheat flour and added fat, sprinkled with salt.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from white wheat flour, flaky cracker style
Description: Commercially prepared, square, plain savoury biscuit made from white wheat flour, with a flaky or layered texture.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from white wheat flour, water cracker style
Description: Commercially prepared round, savoury biscuits made from white wheat flour and water.

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from wholemeal wheat flour, crispbread
Description: Commercially prepared savoury thin, flat, biscuit made from wholemeal wheat flour (plain varieties).

Name: Biscuit, savoury, from wholemeal wheat flour & rye flour, crispbread, puffed
Description: Commercially prepared savoury thin, flat rectangle of puffed, toasted dry bread made from wholemeal wheat flour, some with added bran, malt or rye.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, Anzac style, homemade from basic ingredients
Description: Home prepared crunchy oat biscuit prepared from common household ingredients including rolled oats, wheat flour, coconut, fat and golden syrup.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, biscuit base, mint filling, chocolate-coated
Description: Commercially prepared sweet biscuit, generally chocolate flavoured, sandwiched with sweetened creamy mint filling and coated in chocolate.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, chocolate chip
Description: Commercially prepared sweet biscuit with added chocolate chips.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, plain
Description: Commercially prepared sweet plain biscuit, made without added flavourings, chocolate, fruit or nuts.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, sandwich, cream filling, chocolate-coated
Description: Commercially prepared sweet biscuit, generally chocolate flavoured, sandwiched with sweetened creamy filling and coated in chocolate.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, sandwich, cream & jam filling
Description: Commercially prepared, non-chocolate flavoured sweet biscuit sandwiched with jam and sweetened creamy filling.

Name: Biscuit, sweet, wheatmeal
Description: Commercially prepared sweet biscuit made from wheat flour with added wheatmeal.

Name: Cone, wafer style, for ice cream
Description: Wafer shaped into a cone or similar shape, used for serving ice cream.

Name: Breadcrumbs, white
Description: Crisp crumbs crushed from white bread which has been dried and packaged before sale. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt.

Name: Bread, damper, from white flour, homemade
Description: Round, chemically leavened bread with a thick rough crust and soft inner crumb. Homemade from basic ingredients such as white wheat flour, salt, water or milk and sugar.

Name: Bread, flat, white, commercial
Description: Flat bread made from white wheat flour. Includes a range of styles, including Lebanese, pita, naan, tortillas, mountain bread and wraps. May vary in diameter. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Ready to eat.

Name: Bread, flat (pita or Lebanese), wholemeal, commercial
Description: Double layered, Middle Eastern style flat bread made from wholemeal wheat flour with a small amount of crumb adhering to both crusts. May vary in diameter. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour
Description: Commercially prepared, sliced or unsliced bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added folic acid and iodine, in addition to thiamin. Ready to eat.

Name: Bread, from white flour, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added folic acid and iodine, in addition to thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added calcium
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added calcium, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added calcium, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added calcium, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added fibre
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added fibre and/or added high amylose maize starch, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added fibre, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added fibre and/or added high amylose maize starch, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added iron
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added iron salts, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added iron, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added iron salts, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added omega-3 polyunsaturates
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added omega-3 fatty acids, folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added omega-3 polyunsaturates, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added omega-3 fatty acids, folic acid and iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white Jackaroo flour, added fibre and vitamins B1 & folate & Fe
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten Jackaroo brand bread-making flour specifically formulated in conjunction with the Northern Territory Government. Contains added vitamins B1 and folate, iron and other permitted ingredients.

Name: Bread, from white Jackaroo flour, added fibre and vitamins B1 & folate & Fe, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten Jackaroo brand bread-making flour specifically formulated in conjunction with the Northern Territory Government. Contains added vitamins B1 and folate, iron and other permitted ingredients. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, Italian-style, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared, Italian style bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, Italian-style, commercial, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared, Italian style bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread roll, from white flour
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Dough is shaped into individual serves before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread roll, from white flour, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Dough is shaped into individual serves before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread roll, topped with cheese
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Topped or mixed with grated cheddar cheese.

Name: Bread roll, topped with cheese & bacon
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Topped or mixed with grated cheddar cheese and bacon.

Name: Bread, from wholemeal flour
Description: Commercially prepared, sliced or unsliced bread made from wheat flour containing all the milled constituents of the wheat grain. Contains added folic acid, iodine and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from wholemeal flour, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared sliced or unsliced bread made from wheat flour containing all the milled constituents of the wheat grain. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from wholemeal flour, extra grainy & seeds
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from wholemeal wheat flour with added kibbled grains (including rye, wheat, corn, buckwheat, triticale, purple wheat, millet, oats, and barley) and seeds (including linseed, sunflower and sesame seeds). Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from wholemeal flour, extra grainy & seeds, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from wholemeal wheat flour with added kibbled grains (including rye, wheat, corn, buckwheat, triticale, purple wheat, millet, oats, and barley) and seeds (including linseed, sunflower and sesame seeds). Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread roll, from wholemeal flour
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from wholemeal, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Dough is shaped into individual serves before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread roll, from wholemeal flour, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from wholemeal, wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. Dough is shaped into individual serves before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white or wholemeal flour, organic
Description: Commercially prepared, sliced or unsliced bread made from white, wholemeal or rye wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. May contain added folic acid and iodine, in addition to thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white or wholemeal flour, organic, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared, sliced or unsliced bread made from white, wholemeal or rye wheaten bread-making flour and other permitted ingredients. May contain added folic acid and iodine, in addition to thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, mixed grain
Description: Commercially prepared sliced or unsliced bread made from white and/or wholemeal flour with added kibbled grains. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, mixed grain, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared sliced or unsliced bread made from white and/or wholemeal flour with added kibbled grains. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, extra grainy & seeds
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white wheaten flour with added kibbled grains (including rye, wheat, corn, buckwheat, triticale, purple wheat, millet, oats, and barley) and seeds (including linseed, sunflower and sesame seeds). Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, extra grainy & seeds, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white wheaten flour with added kibbled grains (including rye, wheat, corn, buckwheat, triticale, purple wheat, millet, oats, and barley) and seeds (including linseed, sunflower and sesame seeds). Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread roll, mixed grain
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white and/or wholemeal flour with added kibbled grains. Dough shaped into a single serve before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread roll, mixed grain, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white and/or wholemeal flour with added kibbled grains. Dough shaped into a single serve before baking. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, Turkish
Description: Commercial yeast leavened, thin, soft-crusted white bread typically prepared from white wheat flour, olive oil, water, yeast, sugar, salt and sesame seeds. Contains added folic acid, iodised  salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from white flour, Turkish, toasted
Description: Commercial yeast leavened, thin, soft-crusted white bread typically prepared from white flour, olive oil, water, yeast, sugar, salt and sesame seeds. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from white flour, added dried fruit
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white wheat flour and containing 10- 25% added dried fruit. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, from wheat flour, added dried fruit, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from white wheat flour and containing 10- 25% added dried fruit. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, garlic or herb, commercial, cooked
Description: Commercially prepared white bread to which a garlic or herb butter mixture is added, before the bread is heated usually by baking to melt the butter mixture. Bread contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Bread, garlic or herb, homemade, cooked
Description: Sliced white bread to which a mixture of fat (butter/dairy blend or margarine) and garlic and/or herbs are added, before the bread is heated to melt the fat mixture. Bread contains added folic acid and iodised salt. Cooked by baking, toasting or heating in a microwave.

Name: Bread, gluten free
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from grains other than wheat such as buckwheat groats, cornmeal, rice and quinoa. May contain added folic acid and iodised salt. Ready to eat.

Name: Bread, gluten free, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared bread made from grains other than wheat such as buckwheat groats, cornmeal, rice and quinoa. May contain added folic acid and iodised salt. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bread, from rye flour, sour dough
Description: Commercially prepared sour dough made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and rye flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added thiamin, folic acid and iodised salt.

Name: Bread, from rye flour, sour dough, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared sour dough bread made from white, wheaten bread-making flour and rye flour and other permitted ingredients. Contains added thiamin, folic acid and iodised salt. Cooked by toasting after purchase.

Name: Bun, sweet, with dried fruit, uniced
Description: Commercially prepared sweet bun made from yeasted wheat flour, containing added dried fruit, with sugar glaze on the top. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt.

Name: Bun, sweet, with dried fruit, iced
Description: Commercially prepared sweet bun based on yeasted wheat flour dough and containing added dried fruit, topped with sugar based icing. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt

Name: Crumpet, from white flour, toasted
Description: Commercially prepared, batter-based product containing white, wheat flour, approximately 10 cm diameter and 1cm thick. Batter is leavened with yeast or with chemical agents and contains added salt and preservatives. Cooked on one side only and has an open honeycomb structure on the top surface. Contains added folic acid. Toasted until lightly brown.

Name: Muffin, English style, from white flour
Description: A round yeasted dough made from white wheat flour (approximately 8.5 cm in diameter and 2 cm thick) that has been baked. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt.

Name: Muffin, English style, from white flour, toasted
Description: A round yeasted dough made from white wheat flour (approximately 8.5 cm in diameter and 2 cm thick) that has been baked. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt. Cooked by toasting after purchase until lightly brown.

Name: Muffin, English style, from white flour, added dried fruit, toasted
Description: A round yeasted dough made from white wheat flour with added dried fruit and spice (approximately 8 cm in diameter and 2 cm thick) that has been baked. Contains added folic acid and iodised salt. Cooked by toasting after purchase until lightly brown.

Name: Breakfast cereal, beverage, non-chocolate flavours, added vitamins A, B1, B2, B3, B6, B12, C & folate & Ca
Description: Breakfast cereal beverage made from filtered water, breakfast cereal, skim milk powder, cane sugar, soy protein, sunflower oil, flavours (except chocolate) and added vitamins A, B1, B2, B3, B6, B12, C and folic acid and calcium.

Name: Breakfast cereal, flakes of corn, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from flakes of corn with added salt and sugar. Does not contain added vitamins or minerals.

Name: Breakfast cereal, flakes of corn, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C & folate, Fe & Zn
Description: Breakfast cereal made from flakes of corn with added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C and folic acid, iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, mixed grain (rice & wheat), flakes, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6 & folate, Ca, Fe & Zn
Description: Breakfast cereal made from flakes of lightly toasted rice and wheat grains with sugar and salt added. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6 and folic acid and calcium, iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, mixed grain (wheat & oat), flakes, apricot & sultana, added vitamins B1, B2, B3 & folate & Fe
Description: Breakfast cereal made from flakes of wheat, oats and triticale with dried sultanas, apricot, sugar and salt. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3 and folic acid and iron.

Name: Breakfast cereal, mixed grain (wheat, oat & corn), extruded, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, C & folate, Ca & Fe
Description: Breakfast cereal made from wheat, oatmeal and maize flour with added sugar and salt extruded into various shapes before packaging. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, C and folic acid and calcium and iron.

Name: Breakfast cereal, mixed grain (wheat, rice & oat), flakes, honey, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from flakes of wheat, oats, rice and triticale with added honey, sugar and salt. Does not contain any added vitamins and minerals.

Name: Breakfast cereal, puffed or popped rice, no added sugar or salt, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from toasted puffed or popped rice grains. Does not contain added salt, sugar, vitamins or minerals.

Name: Breakfast cereal, puffed or popped rice, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C & folate, Fe & Zn
Description: Breakfast cereal made from toasted puffed or popped rice grains with added salt and sugar. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C and folic acid and iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, puffed or popped rice, cocoa coating, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C & folate, Ca, Fe & Zn
Description: Chocolate sweetened puffed rice cereal with added sugar and salt. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, C and folic acid, and calcium, iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, wheat bran, flakes, sultanas, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6 & folate, Fe & Zn
Description: Breakfast cereal made from wheat bran flakes with added sultanas. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6 and folic acid and iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, wheat bran, pellets, added vitamins B1, B2 & folate
Description: Breakfast cereal made from wheat bran and extruded into pellets. Contains added vitamins B1, B2 and folic acid.

Name: Breakfast cereal, whole wheat, biscuit, no added sugar, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from whole wheat and salt formed into a biscuit shape. Does not contain any added sugar, vitamins or minerals.

Name: Breakfast cereal, whole wheat, biscuit, added vitamins B1, B2, B3 & folate, Fe & Zn
Description: Breakfast cereal prepared from whole wheat, with added sugar formed into a biscuit shape. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3 and folic acid and iron and zinc.

Name: Breakfast cereal, whole wheat, biscuit, bran, added vitamins B1, B2, B3 & folate & Fe
Description: Breakfast cereal made from whole wheat, with added bran and sugar formed into a biscuit shape. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3 and folic acid and iron.

Name: Breakfast cereal, whole wheat, flakes, dried fruit & nuts, added fibre, vitamins B1, B2, B3 & folate, Ca & Fe
Description: Breakfast cereal made from whole wheat flakes with added wheat bran, dried fruit, nuts and salt. Contains added fibre, vitamins B1, B2, B3 and folic acid and calcium and iron.

Name: Breakfast cereal, whole wheat, puffed, no added sugar or salt, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from puffed whole wheat. Does not contain any added sugar, salt or vitamins or minerals.

Name: Muesli, toasted, added dried fruit & nuts, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from rolled oats, dried fruit and other ingredients such as nuts, coconut and seeds, and then toasted with the addition of vegetable oil. Does not contain added vitamins or minerals.

Name: Muesli, untoasted or natural style, added dried fruit, unfortified
Description: Breakfast cereal made from rolled oats, dried fruit (including sultanas, currants, apricot, pawpaw, banana, apple and pineapple) and other ingredients including wheat bran, wheat germ, sugar, and/or seeds. Includes mueslis with a small amount of added nuts (less than 3%) including almond, coconut, walnut, hazelnut and pecans. Does not contain added vitamins or minerals.

Name: Bread, banana
Description: Sweet, moist cake-like bread made using mashed bananas and other common ingredients such as wheat flour, shortening, sugar and egg.

Name: Slice, brownie, chocolate, without nuts, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared densely textured chocolate slice.

Name: Slice, brownie, chocolate, with nuts, homemade
Description: Home prepared densely textured chocolate slice containing chopped nuts.

Name: Cake mix, plain, dry powder
Description: Commercially prepared dry plain cake mix. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, maize starch, sugar, salt, dairy products, vegetable oils, flavours, colours and baking agents. Includes cake mixes labelled as madeira, tea cake or vanilla cake.

Name: Cake, carrot, commercial, iced
Description: Commercially prepared carrot cake with icing generally made with cream or neufchatel cheese.

Name: Cake, carrot, homemade, uniced
Description: Home prepared carrot cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, butter, sugar, eggs, carrot, sultanas, nuts and spices.

Name: Cake, carrot, homemade, iced
Description: Home prepared carrot cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, butter, sugar, eggs, carrot, sultanas, nuts and spices, with icing.

Name: Cake, chocolate, homemade, uniced
Description: Home prepared chocolate cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, butter, sugar, egg, milk and cocoa.

Name: Cake, chocolate, homemade, iced
Description: Home prepared chocolate cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, butter, sugar, egg, milk and cocoa, with icing.

Name: Cake, fruit, homemade, uniced
Description: Home prepared fruit cake made from common household ingredients such as boiled dried vine fruit, flour, sugar, butter, eggs and citrus peel.

Name: Cake, lamington, unfilled
Description: Commercially prepared individual sponge cube, coated in chocolate icing and coconut.

Name: Cake, mud, dark chocolate, commercial, chocolate ganache icing
Description: Commercially prepared rich chocolate cake, with chocolate icing. Includes cakes commonly described as dark chocolate mud cakes.

Name: Cake, mud, dark chocolate, homemade, uniced
Description: Home prepared heavy textured chocolate cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, sugar, eggs, butter and dark chocolate.

Name: Cake, mud, dark chocolate, homemade, chocolate ganache icing
Description: Home prepared heavy textured chocolate cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, sugar, eggs, butter and dark chocolate, with a rich chocolate ganache icing.

Name: Cake, plain butter cake, commercial, uniced
Description: Commercially prepared plain butter style cake.

Name: Cake, plain butter cake, commercial, iced
Description: Commercially prepared plain butter style cake, with icing.

Name: Cake, plain butter cake, homemade, uniced
Description: Home prepared plain butter cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, butter, sugar and eggs.

Name: Cake, plain butter cake, homemade, iced
Description: Home prepared plain butter cake made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, butter, sugar and eggs, with icing.

Name: Cake, sponge, plain, commercial, uniced, unfilled
Description: Commercially prepared light sponge cake prepared with minimal added fat and with a significant proportion of eggs.

Name: Cake, sponge, plain, commercial, uniced, filled with jam & cream
Description: Commercially prepared light sponge cake prepared with minimal added fat and with a significant proportion of eggs, with a jam and cream filling.

Name: Doughnut, jam filled, sugar coated
Description: Batter shaped into a ball which as been deep fried. A small amount of jam is then injected into the centre and the doughnut dusted with sugar and cinnamon.

Name: Doughnut, dusted with cinnamon & sugar
Description: Sweet batter extruded into a ring shape which has been deep fried in oil and dusted with cinnamon and sugar after cooking.

Name: Doughnut, iced
Description: Sweet batter extruded into a ring shape which has been deep fried in oil, and iced after cooking.

Name: Muffin, cake-style, berry, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared cake style muffin with added berries, such as blueberries and raspberries.

Name: Muffin, cake-style, chocolate chip, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared cake style muffin with added chocolate chips.

Name: Pancake, plain, homemade
Description: Home prepared batter made from common household ingredients such as milk, wheat flour and egg. The batter is poured onto a buttered hotplate and cooked until the batter is set.

Name: Pikelet or pancake, sweet, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared pikelet. Contains added folic acid, iodised salt and thiamin.

Name: Pikelet, plain, homemade
Description: Home prepared batter, made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, egg and sugar. The batter is spooned onto a greased hotplate and cooked until batter is set.

Name: Pudding, chocolate, homemade
Description: Home prepared cake-style chocolate pudding made from common household ingredients such as flour, cocoa, sugar, milk, water and butter, then baked.

Name: Pudding, plum, steamed or boiled, homemade
Description: Home prepared steamed or boiled pudding, made from commonly household ingredients such as dried fruit, candied fruit peel, brandy, flour, sugar, eggs, butter and spices. Most commonly consumed at Christmas time.

Name: Pudding, sticky date, homemade
Description: Home prepared cake-style dessert with caramel sauce made from common household ingredients such as flour, butter, sugar, eggs, milk, chopped dates and spices.

Name: Scone, plain, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared, dough-like product made from flour, water, sugar, fat and a raising agent.

Name: Scone, plain, homemade
Description: Home prepared dough-like product made from common household ingredients such as flour, milk, sugar, fat, egg and a raising agent.

Name: Scone, fruit, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared, dough-like product made from flour, water, sugar, fat, egg, fruit such as sultanas, dates and currants and a raising agent.

Name: Scone, pumpkin, homemade
Description: Dough-like product made from white wheat flour, milk, sugar, fat, egg and raising agent to which mashed pumpkin is added before baking.

Name: Slice, caramel
Description: Sweet slice made from ingredients such as flour, coconut, sugar, butter, condensed milk, golden syrup and chocolate. The slice has a biscuit-style base, firm caramel filling and hard chocolate top.

Name: Buckwheat groats, cooked in water, no added salt
Description: Buck wheat, hulled, crushed, roasted kernels, used in a similar manner to rice. Cooked in unsalted water without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Porridge, rolled oats, prepared with regular fat cows milk
Description: Rolled oats prepared according to label directions. Milk includes fortified and unfortified varieties. Cooked on the stove top or by microwaving.

Name: Amaranth, grain, whole, uncooked
Description: Very small, round grains, with a light sandy/beige colour.

Name: Barley, pearl, uncooked
Description: Grain that has had the bran removed, then is steamed and polished. Uncooked.

Name: Barley, pearl, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Grain that has had the bran removed, then is steamed and polished. Prepared by boiling in unsalted water until tender without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Buckwheat groats, uncooked
Description: Hulled, crushed, roasted kernels, used in a similar manner to rice. Uncooked.

Name: Bulgur, uncooked
Description: A quick-cooking form of whole wheat that has been cleaned, parboiled, dried, ground into particles and sifted into distinct sizes (fine, medium and course grinds). As purchased, not cooked.

Name: Bulgur, soaked in water, no added fat or salt
Description: A quick-cooking form of whole wheat that have been cleaned, parboiled, dried, ground into particles and sifted into distinct sizes (fine, medium and course grinds). Prepared by soaking in unsalted water.

Name: Cornmeal (polenta), uncooked
Description: A type of flour ground from dried kernels of yellow or white corn. Uncooked.

Name: Cornmeal (polenta), boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: A type of flour ground from dried kernels of yellow or white corn. Cooked in unsalted water without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Couscous, uncooked
Description: Cream coloured pellets made from approximately 2 parts semolina, 1 part wheat flour and salt and water, then steamed and dried. No further cooking.

Name: Couscous, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Cream coloured pellets, made from approximately 2 parts semolina, 1 part wheat flour and salt and water, then steamed and dried. Subsequently cooked by soaking in boiling water, without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Millet, uncooked
Description: Uncooked hulled cereal grain.

Name: Millet, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Hulled cereal grain, cooked in water by the absorption method, without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Maize, grits, uncooked
Description: Small, yellow, broken grains of corn.

Name: Oats, hulled, uncooked
Description: A tan coloured, oval-shaped, cylindrical grain that have had their outer husk removed. Uncooked.

Name: Oats, rolled, uncooked
Description: Crushed grain produced by steaming and flattening with hot rollers. No further cooking. Includes traditional and quick cooking styles.

Name: Porridge, rolled oats, prepared with water
Description: Crushed grain produced by steaming and flattening the oats with rollers. Cooked by boiling in unsalted water.

Name: Oats, rolled, mixed with sugar or honey & other flavours, uncooked
Description: Quick cooking rolled oats, sold mixed with honey and sugar and other flavours to be used to prepare a hot, porridge-style breakfast dish. Uncooked.

Name: Psyllium, uncooked
Description: Husk of a small seed which is high in dietary fibre. Uncooked

Name: Quinoa, black, uncooked
Description: Small black seed which has a light, fluffy texture when cooked. Mild and slightly nutty flavour. Uncooked

Name: Quinoa, red, uncooked
Description: Small rusty red seed which has a light, fluffy texture when cooked. Mild and slightly nutty flavour. Uncooked

Name: Quinoa, white, uncooked
Description: Small beige seed which has a light, fluffy texture when cooked. Mild and slightly nutty flavour. Uncooked

Name: Quinoa, uncooked
Description: Small beige, red or black seed which has a light, fluffy texture when cooked. Mild and slightly nutty flavour.

Name: Quinoa, cooked in water, no added salt
Description: Small beige seed which has a light, fluffy texture when cooked. Mild and slightly nutty flavour. Cooked in unsalted water without the addition of fat, oil or salt.

Name: Rye, grain, whole, uncooked
Description: Small, oval-shaped brown grains. Uncooked, unmilled.

Name: Rye, rolled, uncooked
Description: Crushed grain produced by steaming and flattening with hot rollers. Uncooked.

Name: Sorghum, grain, uncooked
Description: Small, round grain that is orange-red in colour. Can be milled into flour or kibbled (cut into) 3 or 4 pieces.

Name: Triticale, grain, uncooked
Description: A beige coloured, long, oval-shaped grain that is a wheat-rye hybrid. Can be milled into flour or kibbled (cut) into 3 or 4 pieces.

Name: Semolina, uncooked
Description: Coarsely ground starchy product from the inner endosperm of durum wheat. It is granular in appearance and ranges from clear to yellow in colour. Uncooked.

Name: Semolina, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Coarsely ground starchy product from the inner endosperm of durum wheat. It is granular in appearance and ranges from clear to yellow in colour. Cooked in unsalted water without the addition of fat or salt.

Name: Spelt, uncooked
Description: Small uncooked grain from the wheat family. Uncooked.

Name: Spelt, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Small uncooked grain from the wheat family. Uncooked.

Name: Tapioca, pearl or seed style, uncooked
Description: Starchy product from the cassava plant supplied in the form of small pellets (also known as seeds or pearls). Sometimes sold labelled as Sago tapioca or Sago. Imported into Australia. Uncooked.

Name: Tapioca, pearl or seed style, boiled, no added fat or salt
Description: Starchy product supplied in the form of small pellets (also known as seeds or pearls). Sometimes sold labelled as Sago tapioca or Sago. Cooked by boiling according to label instructions.

Name: Wheat, whole, uncooked
Description: Whole wheat grain including the bran, germ and endosperm.

Name: Wheat bran, unprocessed, uncooked
Description: Outer layers of the wheat grain which are removed during the early stages of milling, and do not undergo further processing other than packaging. Maybe coarsely or finely milled. Uncooked.

Name: Wheat germ
Description: Small creamy flakes milled from the core of the wheat kernel.

Name: Rice, white, uncooked
Description: Grain that has had its husk, bran and germ removed. The grains after milling have a slight off-white colour. Uncooked.

Name: Rice, white, boiled or rice cooker, no added salt
Description: Grain that has had its husk, bran and germ removed. Cooked by boiling on the stove top or in an electric rice cooker in unsalted water.

Name: Rice, white, purchased as 'instant', microwaved
Description: Grain that has had its husk, bran and germ removed. Pre-cooked before purchase, then heated in the microwave.

Name: Rice, white, fried with bacon or ham, egg, prawns & vegetables
Description: Commercially prepared fried rice with egg, ham or pork, prawns, peas and shallots, ready to eat. As purchased from Chinese restaurants.

Name: Rice, brown, uncooked
Description: Grain with only the inedible outer husk removed. The bran coating gives it a light tan colour. Uncooked.

Name: Rice, brown, boiled, no added salt
Description: Grain with only the inedible outer husk removed. Cooked by boiling in unsalted water.

Name: Rice, wild, uncooked
Description: A long-grain marsh grass. Uncooked.

Name: Rice, wild, boiled, no added salt
Description: A long-grain marsh grass. Cooked by boiling in unsalted water.

Name: Rice paper wrapper, soaked in water
Description: Thin edible paper used to prepare rice paper rolls or summer rolls, typically made from rice flour, salt and water. Sold dried in thin, translucent round or square sheets that are crisp to the touch. Soaked in water with no added oil or salt. Does not contain any fillings.

Name: Flour, arrowroot
Description: Flour ground from the starchy roots of a number of tropical plants.

Name: Flour, cornflour, from maize starch
Description: Fine white powder extracted from the starchy endosperm of maize (corn).

Name: Flour, cornflour, from maize & wheat starch
Description: Fine white powder extracted from the starchy endosperm of maize (corn) or wheat. Sold in Australia under the name of cornflour.

Name: Flour, chickpea (besan)
Description: Flour prepared from dried, ground chick peas.

Name: Flour, rice
Description: Flour ground from grains of white and/or brown rice.

Name: Flour, rye
Description: A flour made from the milled wholegrain of rye.

Name: Flour, soya
Description: Creamy, finely ground flour processed from soya beans.

Name: Flour, spelt
Description: Flour prepared from ground spelt, a type of wheat.

Name: Flour, wheat, white, plain
Description: Flour prepared from ground wheat from which bran has been removed. No added vitamins,  minerals or leavening agents.

Name: Flour, wheat, white, plain, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, E & folate & Fe, Mg & Zn (Jackaroo)
Description: Flour prepared from ground wheat from which bran has been removed. Specifically formulated in conjunction with the Northern Territory Government. Contains added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, E and folate, iron, magnesium and zinc.

Name: Flour, wheat, white, self-raising
Description: Flour prepared from ground wheat from which bran has been removed. Chemical leavening agents added. No added vitamins or minerals.

Name: Flour, wheat, white, self-raising, added vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, E & folate & Fe, Mg & Zn (Jackaroo)
Description: Flour prepared from ground wheat from which bran has been removed. Specifically formulated in conjunction with the Northern Territory Government. Contains added chemical leavening agents and vitamins B1, B2, B3, B6, E and folate, iron, magnesium and zinc.

Name: Flour, wheat, white, high protein or bread making flour
Description: High protein wheat flour which may contain added gluten to achieve a protein content ranging from 12-16%. Suitable for use in bread making. Contains added thiamin and folic acid.

Name: Flour, wheat, wholemeal, plain
Description: Flour milled from whole wheat grain (bran, germ and flour). No added vitamins, minerals or leavening agents.

Name: Flour, gluten free, plain
Description: Flour mix prepared from white gluten free starches and flours including rice, tapioca and corn/maize.

Name: Flour, wheat, wholemeal, self-raising
Description: Flour milled from whole wheat grain (bran, germ and flour) to which chemical leavening agents have been added. No added vitamins or minerals.

Name: Hamburger, white roll, beef patty, with cheese, onion, pickles & sauce, fast food chain
Description: Commercially prepared hamburger containing a grilled beef burger patty, with processed cheese, pickles, sauce and onion in white bread roll, as served in fast food chains.

Name: Hamburger, white roll, beef patty, with salad, independent takeaway outlet
Description: Commercially prepared hamburger containing a grilled or pan fried beef burger patty and salad in a white bread roll, as served from an independent takeaway outlet.

Name: Hot dog, bread roll, frankfurt & sauce filling
Description: Fresh bread or bread roll containing a frankfurt, sauce and/or mustard.

Name: Pizza, cheese & tomato, commercial
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce and cheese. Includes frozen, fast food and takeaway styles.

Name: Pizza, ham & pineapple, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce, cheese, ham and pineapple, frozen before packaging and reheated prior to consumption.

Name: Pizza, ham & pineapple, takeaway style
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce, cheese, ham and pineapple. Purchased ready to eat from independent takeaway food outlets.

Name: Pizza, supreme, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce, cheese, sausage, capsicum, onion, ham, mushrooms and sometimes olives and beef, frozen before packaging and reheated prior to consumption.

Name: Pizza, supreme, fast food chain
Description: Commercially produced thick pizza dough typically topped with tomato-based sauce, cheese, ground beef, mushrooms, onion, capsicum, pepperoni, pineapple and ham/bacon. Purchased ready to eat from fast food outlets.

Name: Pizza, supreme, takeaway style
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce, cheese, sausage, capsicum, onion, ham, anchovies, olives, beef, mushrooms and sometimes prawns. Purchased ready to eat from independent takeaway food outlets.

Name: Pizza, vegetable, fast food chain
Description: Commercially produced pizza dough topped with tomato-based sauce and a mixture of vegetables. Purchased ready to eat from fast food outlets.

Name: Noodle, soba, dry
Description: Commercially prepared dry noodles made from a mix of wheat and buckwheat flour. Uncooked.

Name: Noodle, soba, boiled, drained
Description: Commercially prepared dry noodles made from a mix of wheat and buckwheat flour, boiled in unsalted water and then drained.

Name: Noodle, wheat, fresh, soaked, drained
Description: Commercially prepared, moist, wheat based noodle, commonly used in Asian style cooking. Includes noodles described as Hokkien, Singapore and Chow Mein noodles. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt.

Name: Noodle, wheat, instant, flavoured, dry, uncooked
Description: Commercially prepared noodle made from wheat flour, vegetable oil, salts and vegetable gums, coiled into blocks and dried before packaging. Includes contents of flavour sachet. Uncooked.

Name: Noodle, wheat, instant, flavoured, boiled, drained
Description: Commercially prepared noodle made from wheat flour, vegetable oil, salts and vegetable gums, coiled into blocks and dried before packaging. Cooked by heating in boiling water with contents of favour sachet. Drained of excess water.

Name: Noodle, wheat, instant, flavoured, boiled, undrained
Description: Commercially prepared noodle made from wheat flour, vegetable oil, salts and vegetable gums, coiled into blocks and dried before packaging. Cooked by heating in boiling water with contents of favour sachet. Undrained of excess water.

Name: Noodle, rice stick, boiled, drained
Description: Commercially prepared noodles made from a paste of water and ground rice, or rice with cornflour, which are then dried and coiled. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt and then drained.

Name: Pasta, gluten free, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made from grains other than wheat such corn and rice with added water. Cooked in boiling water without added salt or fat until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Pasta, maize flour (corn) based, dry
Description: The dough made by combining maize flour with water. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Uncooked.

Name: Pasta, maize flour (corn) based, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made by combining maize flour with water. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour, dry
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum semolina) with water. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum semolina) with water. Cooked in boiling water without added salt or fat until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour, fresh, uncooked
Description: Commercial product prepared from white wheat flour and other ingredients and cut to shape, but not dried prior to packaging. Includes fresh pasta containing egg. Uncooked.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour, fresh, boiled, no added salt
Description: Commercial product prepared from white wheat flour and other ingredients and cut to shape, but not dried prior to packaging. Includes fresh pasta containing egg. Boiled without added salt or fat, although the pasta itself is likely to contain added salt.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour & egg, dry
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum wheat) with eggs. The dough is then dried prior to sale.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour & egg, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum wheat) with eggs. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour & spinach, dry
Description: The dough made by combining white wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum wheat) with water and spinach. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Uncooked.

Name: Pasta, white wheat flour & spinach, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made by combining white wheat flour or semolina (preferably durum wheat) with water and spinach. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Pasta, wholemeal wheat flour, dry
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour (with varying proportions of whole-wheat grain and white flour) or semolina (preferably durum semolina) with water. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Uncooked.

Name: Pasta, wholemeal wheat flour, boiled from dry, no added salt
Description: The dough made by combining wheat flour (with varying proportions of whole-wheat grain and white flour) or semolina (preferably durum semolina) with water. The dough is then dried before packaging and sale. Cooked by boiling without added fat or salt until firm to the bite. Drained.

Name: Lasagne, beef, commercial, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially prepared pasta dish made from layers of minced beef, tomato sauce filling, savoury white cheese sauce and pasta. Purchased frozen, then baked at home before consumption.

Name: Lasagne, beef, homemade
Description: Home prepared pasta dish made from layers of pasta, bolognese sauce with added vegetables, savoury white cheese sauce and cheese (typically cheddar/mozzarella/parmesan).

Name: Macaroni & cheese, homemade, cooked unfilled pasta, homemade cheese sauce
Description: Home prepared pasta dish made from macaroni pasta, and a cheese based sauce commonly containing cheddar cheese, parmesan cheese, cream and milk.

Name: Pasta in cream based sauce, dry mix
Description: Commercially packaged product that contains dry pasta mixed with dry ingredients that, when reconstituted with liquid, will form a cream-style dish. Includes mixes described as carbonara or sour cream style. Typical ingredients include pasta, cheese, whey and skim milk powder, salt, spices and colours.

Name: Pasta in cream based sauce, prepared from dry mix with regular fat milk cows & margarine spread
Description: Pasta meal prepared from a commercial dry mix by the addition of regular fat cows milk, water and margarine spread. Made according to package instructions.

Name: Spaghetti in tomato & cheese sauce, canned
Description: Commercially prepared canned pasta product containing spaghetti in tomato and cheese sauce.

Name: Spaghetti in tomato & cheese sauce, canned, reduced salt
Description: Commercially prepared canned pasta product containing spaghetti in a reduced salt tomato and cheese sauce.

Name: Croissant, plain
Description: Commercially prepared crescent-shaped pastry prepared from ingredients such as wheat flour, butter, yeast, sugar, egg, milk powder and food additives, then baked. Sodium content likely to vary widely depending on ingredients.

Name: Pastry, filo, commercial, raw
Description: Uncooked commercial thin sheets of wheat flour based pastry, prepared without added fat, used in preparation of strudels and Greek-style pastry dishes.

Name: Pastry, filo, commercial, baked
Description: Baked commercial thin sheets of wheat flour based pastry, prepared without added fat, used in preparation of strudels and Greek-style pastry dishes.

Name: Pastry, puff, with butter, commercial, raw
Description: Uncooked pastry purchased ready-to-cook from supermarkets. Pastry may be sold in thin sheets or in blocks that need to be rolled. Produces a pastry that contains multiple fine layers and is often used on the top of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, butter, salt, citric acid and preservative.

Name: Pastry, puff, with butter, commercial, baked
Description: Pastry purchased uncooked from supermarkets and then baked at home. Pastry may be sold in thin sheets or in blocks that need to be rolled. Produces a pastry that contains multiple fine layers and is often used on the top of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, butter, salt, citric acid and preservative.

Name: Pastry, puff, vegetable oil, commercial, raw
Description: Uncooked pastry purchased ready-to-cook from supermarkets. Pastry may be sold in thin sheets or in blocks that need to be rolled. Produces a pastry that contains multiple fine layers and is often used on the top of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, vegetable oil, salt, citric acid and preservative.

Name: Pastry, puff, vegetable oil, commercial, baked
Description: Pastry purchased uncooked from supermarkets and then baked at home. Pastry may be sold in thin sheets or in blocks that need to be rolled. Produces a pastry that contains multiple fine layers and is often used on the top of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, vegetable oil, salt, citric acid and preservative.

Name: Pastry, shortcrust style, commercial, raw
Description: Uncooked pastry purchased in thin sheets or blocks from supermarkets. Produces a firm pastry often used on the base of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, vegetable fat, glycerol, citric acid and water.

Name: Pastry, shortcrust style, commercial, baked
Description: Pastry purchased in thin sheets or blocks from supermarkets and baked at home. Produces a firm pastry often used on the base of pies. Typical ingredients include wheat flour, vegetable fat, glycerol, citric acid and water.

Name: Pastry, filled with spinach & cheese, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially prepared savoury filo pastry product enclosing a filling of spinach and cheese (generally ricotta or feta), purchased frozen and baked at home.

Name: Pie, savoury, meat, commercial, ready to eat
Description: Commercially prepared meat-based (usually beef and/or mutton) filling enclosed in pastry, purchased ready to eat.

Name: Pie, savoury, meat, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially prepared meat-based (usually beef and/or mutton) filling enclosed pastry, purchased frozen and baked at home.

Name: Sausage roll, commercial, ready to eat
Description: Commercially prepared meat filling (usually beef and/or lamb) rolled in pastry, purchased ready to eat.

Name: Sausage roll, purchased frozen, baked
Description: Commercially prepared meat filling (usually beef and/or lamb) rolled in pastry, purchased frozen, and baked at home.

Name: Spring roll, meat & vegetable filling, commercial, deep fried
Description: Commercially prepared meat and/or vegetable filling rolled in thin pastry, which has been deep fried. Includes spring rolls purchased frozen and served in takeaway food outlets.

Name: Pie, sweet, apple, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared apple filling enclosed in sweet short crust pastry. Purchased ready to eat.

Name: Tart, custard, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared shortcrust pastry shell with a custard filling.

Name: Dressing, French or Italian, regular fat, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared thin sauce used to dress salads. Major ingredients include water, vegetable oil, sugar, vinegar, garlic and spices.

Name: Dressing, thousand island, regular fat, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared thick beige or light orange coloured cream, emulsified sauce used to dress salads and seafood. Major ingredients include vegetable oil, tomato, sugar and gherkin relish.

Name: Gravy powder, dry mix
Description: Dry mix for reconstitution as sauce to be served with meat. Typical ingredients may include wheat flour, salt, colour, spices and vegetable protein.

Name: Gravy, prepared from dry powder with water
Description: Gravy powder prepared with water, according to packet instructions. Typical ingredients may include wheat flour, salt, colour, spices and vegetable protein.

Name: Mayonnaise, traditional (greater than 70% fat), commercial
Description: Commercially prepared white, emulsified sauce with a similar thick consistency to cream. Used in sandwiches or to dress salads. Major ingredients include oil, sugar, vinegar and egg.

Name: Mayonnaise, low fat, commercial
Description: A white, emulsified sauce with a similar thick consistency to cream, using lower levels of oil to develop a product with a low fat content. Used in sandwiches and to dress salads. Major ingredients include oil, sugar and vinegar.

Name: Mustard, cream style
Description: Yellowish paste prepared from ground mustard seeds (typically 10 - 30% of total product), water, vinegar, salt and herbs or other spices. Sold packaged in jars and used as a condiment without further preparation.

Name: Paste, Indian style curry, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared Indian style curry paste sauce. Ingredients may include chilli, lemon grass, garlic, salt, galangal, shrimp paste, kaffir lime, shallots and spices.

Name: Paste, green curry, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared paste containing green chilli, onions, salt, spices, herbs, vegetable oil and other ingredients, used for preparing south-east Asian style main dishes.

Name: Paste, soybean
Description: A thick paste made from fermented and processed soya beans mixed with grain and injected with a yeast mould.

Name: Paste, shrimp
Description: Commercially prepared dark, pungent paste prepared from shrimp and used as a flavouring in Asian style cooking.

Name: Sauce, barbecue, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared sweet, thick, brown coloured, bottled sauce containing apples, sugar, Worcestershire sauce, golden syrup, food acid, thickener, salt, molasses, mixed citrus peel, raisins, spices, vegetable gum and water.

Name: Sauce, butter chicken, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared Indian style butter chicken sauce. Commonly contains water, tomatoes, onions, vegetable oil, cream, butter, sugar, salt, spices, garlic, chilli and colour.

Name: Sauce, cranberry, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared jellied or semi-jellied sweet jam-like sauce made from cranberries, sugars and water.

Name: Sauce, fish, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared sauce based on fish or anchovy extract, and salt, commonly used in Asian style cooking.

Name: Sauce, hoi sin (hoisin), commercial
Description: Commercially prepared sweet, spicy bottled sauce based on fermented soya beans with other ingredients.

Name: Sauce, oyster, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared sauce based on oyster extract, sugar, caramel, salt, starch, flavour, protein or hydrolysed vegetable protein, soy sauce, preservative, sodium benzoate, water, food conditioner. Commonly used in Asian-style cooking.

Name: Sauce, pasta or simmer, commercial, low fat
Description: Commercially prepared sauce for use as a simmer/pasta bake sauce, formulated so as to contain less than 3% fat. Typical ingredients include water, thickener, cheese, onion, garlic, salt, flavours, herbs and spices.

Name: Sauce, pasta, basil pesto, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared basil pesto flavoured pasta sauce. Commonly containing basil, vegetable and /or olive oil, cashews, pine nuts, water, cheese, sugar, salt and garlic.

Name: Sauce, pasta, bolognese, homemade using beef mince & homemade tomato based sauce
Description: Home prepared savoury sauce made from beef mince, onion, garlic, oil, mushroom, and a home-prepared tomato based sauce made from canned tomatoes, tomato paste, stock, pepper, parsley and water. Commonly served with pasta.

Name: Sauce, pasta, cheese or cream-based, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared creamy pasta sauce containing water, cream and/or cheese, thickener, vegetable oil, flavours, salt, herbs and spices. Different flavoured sauces may also contain vegetables, and/or meat products.

Name: Sauce, pasta, tomato-based, commercial, heated
Description: Commercially prepared tomato-based pasta sauce with herbs, spices and vegetables for addition to pasta dishes. Heated without added ingredients according to label instructions.

Name: Sauce, plum, commercial
Description: Commercially prepared chutney-style, spicy, sweet, hot sauce, based on plums.

Name: Sauce, rogan josh, commercial
